## Purpose

The Instance Database contains **working, in-progress** artifacts that are being
developed or modified before promotion to the KDB.

## Structure

```
IDB/
├── drafts/          # Work-in-progress artifacts
├── reviews/         # Artifacts under review
└── staging/         # Artifacts ready for KDB promotion
```

## Rules

- Artifacts in IDB are not authoritative
- Draft artifacts may be incomplete or unvalidated
- Promotion to KDB requires BREX validation and approval
- Superseded copies should be cleaned up regularly
